Quote:  Crush the flax roots and heat the juice in a paua shell - part of the potion is applied to the person's anus, a stalk of kakaho is then filled with the flax potion. The end of the stalk is pushed into the person's anus and the other end is blown so that the potion spurts into the rectum.
